data.description:
*Seller is now offering $4,000 towards buyer's closing costs!!* Welcome to your dream home- 210 Swinton Pond Road! This immaculate, two-story residence built in 2020 offers the perfect blend of modern living and classic charm. Nestled on a coveted corner lot, this property boasts pristine condition, elegant custom features, and breathtaking pond views.

This home is perfectly situated in a wonderful Grovetown neighborhood, offering a tranquil suburban retreat while being conveniently close to shopping, I-20 access, and Fort Eisenhower (formally known as Fort Gordon). Enjoy the unique advantage of a corner lot, which not only provides extra privacy but also adds to the curb appeal of this charming home. Wake up to stunning pond views right from your backyard. This serene backdrop is perfect for unwinding after a long day or entertaining guests on the spacious patio.

Built in 2020, this home is practically brand new and has been meticulously maintained. It's truly move-in ready, sparing you the hassle of renovations or repairs. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining area, and living room, making it easy to spend quality time with family and friends. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring custom cabinets, granite countertops, and a large island. It's an entertainer's delight and a chef's dream come true!

All three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and the laundry room are located on the upper level, ensuring practicality and a peaceful living environment downstairs. The owner's suite is a retreat with its en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Enjoy the elegance of granite countertops in all the bathrooms, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.

This exceptional home is the epitome of modern living in a picturesque setting. Don't miss your chance to call this Grovetown gem your own. Schedule a showing today and be prepared to fall in love with your future home!
